01:16:29.209 --> 01:16:31.046
Junior! Junior. Stop.

01:16:31.046 --> 01:16:33.213
Hey. Hey.
It’s not what you think.

01:16:33.213 --> 01:16:34.918
It’s not what you think.

01:16:37.184 --> 01:16:38.955
Fucking do something.

01:16:46.732 --> 01:16:50.032
