"I wouldn’t dream of it"

01:37:09.987 --> 01:37:14.057
♪ But then I felt
his lips touch mine

01:37:14.057 --> 01:37:16.092
♪ Now I dream of it

01:37:18.193 --> 01:37:22.901
♪ How I dream of it
all the time

01:37:22.901 --> 01:37:29.468
♪ All the time

01:37:29.468 --> 01:37:33.472
♪ I felt him ever
